Global error handling module. Errors of every all the LoS modules may
be handled by it.

EHMessage.java
--------------
    Error message handler. To print out error messages call it like 
    this:
        
        EHMessage.PRINT( error_type )
        
    Note that error_type is must be one of the type registered at 
    Types where are located in 'error_handlers/types' directory.
    
Interfaces
==========

EHMessageInterface.java
-----------------------
    For now, it is used to prefix error messages of each module. 
    Later on, it would be used as library that holds more specific and 
    user-friendly error messages for all the modules.


Types
=====

TEHMonsters.java
----------------
    Type Error Handlers for Monsters. All the error indices of 
    monsters modules are here.
